/a83c9aa60b061fb72c5d508bea739bbd.avif?t=1770109226\" width=614 height=178 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras/f221e128dbdeaebe6f4bbf6c8f11e2ae.avif?t=1770109226\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras_big/f221e128dbdeaebe6f4bbf6c8f11e2ae.avif?t=1770109226 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong>'s here, I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of  <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing all by myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>If you like my works, consider leaving a review here on Steam, your support will be greatly appreciated!</strong></i></p>",
